==English==

===Verb===
'''[[put]] [[to]] the [[test]]'''

#{{idiom}} To [[test]] something or someone; to [[evaluate]], [[scrutinize]] or [[explore]] by testing or [[experimentation]].
#:''He got a new bicycle yesterday, so I expect that today he will want to take it out riding and '''put it to the test'''.''

